Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Through his outstanding ability to control fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan achieved victory over fellow alchemist Lu Mu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming famous in a single battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Xiao Yan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,finally used his strength to repay Xun’er’s faith
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and swore to Xun’er that he would never leave her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how enormous the power behind her was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting is far from over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger opponents had already been eyeing Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This Wu Hao has just hurried back\Nfrom the Black Corner Region, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dense bloody aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this Wu Hao was once one of Xun’er’s suitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, due to your appearance, he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prove
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that Xun’er did not make the wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not going to concede?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,just how strong the Blood Asura actually is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Hao wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Xiao Yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dare come down to fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be interesting;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just who is stronger, this Xiao Yan or the Blood Asura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,only knowing how to hide behind women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully both get injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing me to save some energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is now the Qualifying Competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not a place for private challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the Qualifying Competition’s final day;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at that time, there will naturally be an opportunity for you to fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t disappoint me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that the person Xun’er waited so long for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,isn’t trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The competition will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to know my current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just wait until tomorrow’s competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if you had shown your full power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that opponent today, I’m afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn’t have been able to endure a single exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cousin Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s still the competition tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we will go back to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Mei isn’t a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,En.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all things of the past;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already let go of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate of training progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it’ll probably take another ten days before\NI can reach Six-star Fight Grandmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who it was that abducted you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they must pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This jade piece
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,can actually resist my Green Lotus Core Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what special properties does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am unable to sense
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the aura of the Fallen Heart Flame in Jia Nan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has already been snatched by others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That should not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I am unable to sense its aura for certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by relying on the unique attraction between Heavenly Flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the Bone Chilling Flame has vaguely detected
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that within a thousand miles of the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there remain faint traces of the Fallen Heart Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a thousand miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how long would we have to search for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those old fellows at Jia Nan Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s no way they haven’t become aware\Nof the Fallen Heart Flame’s existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve always felt that the Inner Academy and\NFallen Heart Flame have some relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are able enter the Inner Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we can probably better ascertain the aura’s location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it won’t disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there are far more spectators today\Ncompared to the last two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the final elimination competition to pick five out of twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, nobody wants to miss the most exciting showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, he’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bai Shan! I believe you will definitely be the champion this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your reputation to be destroyed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,this Bai Shan has high achievements in terms of training talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He is quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be careful when you meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Xun’er!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Xun’er.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Xun’er,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,today, we all have to do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter the top five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As for stinky men, forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See how I take care of you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I offend her somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Outer Academy Deputy\NHeadmaster’s granddaughter, Hu Jia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She possesses extremely strong talent that is not inferior to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she has an odd personality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and is very stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,People call her “Little Witch.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This Little Witch sure is macho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Her reputation truly is well-deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that in previous years, the Inner Academy Qualifying\NCompetition consisted entirely of one on one battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever ranks higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the training resources they obtain from\Nnow on will naturally be greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the competition this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we have decided to change the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They changed the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are the Elders thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,can the top twenty students please enter the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All twenty people at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Bai Shan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Hu Jia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hu Jia! My goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we will no longer have single elimination rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather, a battle royale filled with hot blood and excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever can last longer in the competition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,will have a higher ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The other way is also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This change to the rules is way too sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they change the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you fight alone or join hands to attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it is all allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can join hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then wouldn’t we be able to fight side by side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But this kind of mode
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,isn’t necessarily advantageous for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Academy’s most outstanding, like Bai Shan, Hu Jia and Wu Hao,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,are able to find allies more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your prestige in the Academy is quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn’t you also gather up some people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there would indeed be people who come to guard the flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, the flower has an owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just me is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the surging waves ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we will push through together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will announce,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the final elimination round
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how will we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You, follow me in attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, defend against sneak attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Hu Jia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how about I protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t attack carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Headmaster’s idea is not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be completely fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can develop a person’s cautious\Nmentality and ability to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got bored of past one on one battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to try changing things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, for students who are not good at communicating,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in this kind of situation where you are\Nsurrounded by enemies on all sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they will have a harder time, I’m afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have already fallen in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who will be our next opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s your turn at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,hold back Junior Xun’er.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me deal with that Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the ones who should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Xun’er!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t think that just because you defeated Lu Mu, you are able to run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many people stronger than him in Jia Nan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have you, Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,be defeated by me in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are not worthy of Xun’er!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t delay any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Using it so soon..?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking Lightning Arc Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The green colored flame on that Xiao Yan’s body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,should be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a Heavenly Flame, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With a temperature that can cause us to feel heart palpitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it is indeed a Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my Alchemy Department wants him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he does not delay his training at the Inner Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I earnestly wish for the Academy to have another outstanding alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,actually pushing Bai Shan to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That Xiao Yan’s punches are so rapid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he ditched the heavy ruler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Presumably, he normally always carries\Nthe heavy ruler in order to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this guy so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be now, of all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s about to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is interference during advancement,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at best he will be injured, at worst he may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this little fellow will have to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the heavens are helping me.
